{"tid":899923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"統獨議題在台灣都假議題  喊統的不敢真統   喊獨的不敢真獨   國民兩黨都是假話","createTime":"2018-11-12T23:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T05:58:30.000Z","uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"46bb0f1e6e9640a8cea3c6c9007f1e4525d8b045","tid":899923,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T23:55:29.000Z","msg":"國民黨籍蔡正元表示統獨議題在台灣都假議題，喊統的不敢真統，喊獨的不敢真獨<br />\n<br />\nＦＢ內容：<br />\n: 統獨在台灣<br />\n: 都是假議題<br />\n: <span style=\"color: red;\">國民黨是假統一<br />\n: 民進黨是假台獨<br />\n: 兩黨都是假話</span><br />\n: 國民黨談統一<br />\n: 設了一堆條件<br />\n: 說穿了<br />\n: 美國不贊成統一<br />\n: 國民黨也不敢統一<br />\n: 民進黨談台獨<br />\n: 講了一堆廢話<br />\n: 說穿了<br />\n: <span style=\"color: red;\">美國不同意台獨<br />\n: 民進黨就不敢台獨<br />\n: 美國才是真的不統不獨</span><br />\n: 因爲<br />\n: 美國視台灣為勢力範圍<br />\n: 任何黨在台灣執政<br />\n: 都必須是扈從政權<br />\n: 美國用統一呼弄北京<br />\n: 用台獨制衡北京<br />\n: 所以美國操作統獨<br />\n: 不准60度C以上的台獨<br />\n: 也不准40度C以下的台獨<br />\n: 因為60度C太燙<br />\n: 會激怒北京<br />\n: 40度C又太冷<br />\n: 無法制衡北京<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tsaichengyuan/posts/2695809583793284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftsaichengyuan%2Fposts%2F2695809583793284&d=SsN2fCzZsuJIJ9cIHCIj4aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f1185dd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tsaichengyuan/posts/2695809583793284</a>"},{"pid":"8a474ca8e7c076030a4a34ff1ad8db18bce755c5","tid":899923,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:01:23.000Z","msg":"說穿了就是KMT黨章第一條的內容啊幹<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國國民黨黨章<br />\n<br />\n第一條<br />\n中國國民黨（以下簡稱本黨）為民主的、公義的、創新的全民政黨。本黨基於三民主義的理念，<span style=\"color: red;\">建設臺灣地區為民有、民治、民享的社會，實現中華民國為自由、民主、均富和統<br />\n一的國家。標章為，本黨中央黨部設於台北市。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kmt.org.tw/2017/09/blog-post_79.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kmt.org.tw%2F2017%2F09%2Fblog-post_79.html&d=SsN2fCzZsuJIJ9cIHCIj4aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=93c3d7dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.kmt.org.tw/2017/09/blog-post_79.html</a><br />\n當年李登輝將國民黨由革命民主政黨改為民主政黨"},{"pid":"82efeedcedaaadb42681c12f35c5278ac08d84fd","tid":899923,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:21:08.000Z","msg":"總括而言，管治台灣嘅大佬一定係AIT<br />\n選舉就係比藍綠玩下爭凳仔"},{"pid":"5f490d2cf012b9624b94f27eb0af849591b848c6","tid":899923,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82efeedcedaaadb42681c12f35c5278ac08d84fd","tid":899923,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:21:08.000Z","msg":"總括而言，管治台灣嘅大佬一定係AIT<br />\n選舉就係比藍綠玩下爭凳仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:24:21.000Z","msg":"每次總統選舉<br />\n候選人都到美國&quot;面試&quot;"},{"pid":"94c6100e5f2b33a343a0b360d4153dfe0818d677","tid":899923,"uid":54940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:28:03.000Z","msg":"國民黨唔想被統一???有錢收喎"},{"pid":"698b1f067775d59d4a6ae53d95a64128b9dbe5f2","tid":899923,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:29:31.000Z","msg":"手法同香港個班保皇狗打手一樣<br />\n一樣國民黨話不反對統一<br />\n就即刻拉埋對手民進黨落水<br />\n兩邊一齊屌"},{"pid":"2b9742ad838b63a1b97f4f37e08c0caa74e70fa6","tid":899923,"uid":54870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"94c6100e5f2b33a343a0b360d4153dfe0818d677","tid":899923,"uid":54940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:28:03.000Z","msg":"國民黨唔想被統一???有錢收喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:30:34.000Z","msg":"在國民黨的立場<br />\n如果真係統一，自己作為中介就再冇利用價值<br />\n梗係好似依家咁，不統不獨，油水先深"},{"pid":"6945960e1d85e27838045953b3c20d5aa5cbc44a","tid":899923,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:56:41.000Z","msg":"Status quo"},{"pid":"574ca1bb8f9a307cd83dcdb7159171aaacd9a257","tid":899923,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}